divs: Sighting DetailsI was just outside with my camera. I was taking pictures of the moon. I didn't see the unidentified object at the time. Later I was reviewing my pictures and noticed the anomaly, from my position, just to the bottom right of the moon. I am not sure what this is but would like to know. I originally sent the images to the national MUFON but have heard nothing. I am submitting all the shots I have. It is the same picture I just enlarged it.
Summary: Didn't see it until I happened to review the picture and noticed it.
